Friends are coming back home to go to their house and hang out but come across a wishing well and has a keychain stuck on it. One boy picks up a keychain and gets transported inside the wishing well which takes him into another dimension. This dimension has been trapped for several years by the humans who revolted againts them and are hunting on whoever is holding the keychain, which is this friend. He tries to run away from the people who come after him and makes friends along the way.